text: Wabash Avenue is a 1950 American musical movie directed by Henry Koster and starring Betty Grable, Victor Mature, Phil Harris, Reginald Gardiner, James Barton, Barry Kelley, Margaret Hamilton, Jacqueline Dalya, Robin Raymond, Hal K. Dawson, Dorothy Neumann, Alexander Pope, Henry Kulky, Marie Bryant, Collette Lyons, George Beranger. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1951. It was a remake of the 1943 movie Coney Island. == Other websites == * * * Category:1950 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Koster
